Cover: Ian Jackson

This issue is supposedly created by a "skeleton staff" (i.e. of actual skeletons) and the credits are appropriately pseudonymous. As part of this framing story, the Hadrian Vile strip is deliberately printed upside down and "Pete's Pup" is mistitled as "Fred's Fish".
